Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.82,0:01:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,請便
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,小伙子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你們準備一張輪椅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 立刻準備
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:02:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,大家早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,睡個好覺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不過睡得還湊合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧你們 我睡得很香喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來母親的儀式好像要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,大家也會去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,尚城不拒絕任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,無論何人都會給予他生活的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣一個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是為了讓大家開心才被呼喚來到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,吃驚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼爾 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,大家可以自由參加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是宗教嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:03:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡的人都是被母親的能力吸引過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,聚集在一起而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人就是母親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來將要舉行和死者的會面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,死者?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,母親她可以與死人對話喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼胡話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.47,0:03:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能 這太扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有母親那種能力的人被稱為靈媒師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,靈媒師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,指的是死後世界與現世之間的媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就是半熟和全熟的中間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,被選中的參加者請到顏之間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,去跟上那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:03:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 剛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,想看儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼是用金繕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不是為了復原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,注入新的生命讓它延續
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,才是我們的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,死者的儀式也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,死者無法復活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,可是知曉死者想法的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可以借助大地大人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,與死者連接並使對話成立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,然後倖存者將開始新的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這股氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,大麻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:04:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那是大地大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,尚城的標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,以大地大人作為媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可以讓母親使用出能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,難道10歲的是他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不久將舉辦誕生10周年的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這個是遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,佳惠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳救了被海嘯捲走的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,密碼就在金庫的裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,替我活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我會一直守護著妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這是父親的鐘錶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真也 喂 真也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你能聽到我說的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在倒塌的屋子裡我說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,丟下我自己跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要是連你也死掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,像大峽谷一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這是琵琶湖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,湖底出現了一條巨大的裂縫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,水就流了進去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼多的水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想和爸爸說話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,總之就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我認為不是誰都能夠參加儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 這裡能夠看到菲律賓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,開個玩笑 嚇到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,才不會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 妳也笑起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,大家來拍張照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.69,0:07:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才那個儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎麼做才能被選上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,根據天啟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那是騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,請勿靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,信不信是你的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這個是某個男子的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,妳摸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,想要與死者見面請根據順序
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我在和母親講話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,母親一天只能會見三人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,請回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,想休息的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那個女孩是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是七海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,剛 全部吃掉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我會吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這是哪裡的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,南斯拉夫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小時候經常吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:08:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,多吃點多吃點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這是科索沃的名菜燉肉湯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnAvenir Next W1G\b1\pos(793,668)}Paçe
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,新來的 來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,偏食對健康不好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不想被胖子說健康問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,吃了飯就去上學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡有學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有喔 雖然也就幾十個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,剛 步 今天開始去上學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,大家要是想工作的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,也儘管說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,還有很多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在三角形abc中 邊bc為底邊時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,頂點a到底邊bc的垂線長度為三角形的高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好多大麻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,工作真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的就拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛很癢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,地震?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,難道你是知道地震會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 不會這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,學校如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,日本人太多了很無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,挑三揀四可不好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,力士什錦火鍋 知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,力士吃的那個東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 你喜歡相撲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,沒興趣 大谷先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我是非常喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得我能成為職業力士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 只是身體大是贏不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,剛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,和爸爸對話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,摩斯電碼 隨便做了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸絕對看得見的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,想聽爸爸的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不行?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕爸爸會胡言亂語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,還有可能生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事 反正你也猜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,火好像熄滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我去借個打火機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧了母親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我心中的陰霾已經不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是也要參加比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很多人都在說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,要去派對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,據說是週末的派對 在今晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我被邀請過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,已經熄滅了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,換你來吹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 著起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是沒熄滅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.78,0:13:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,頭髮長長了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 媽媽妳不去派對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不習慣去吵鬧的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是很想聽爸爸的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽不想聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 不想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,因為沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,其實妳是想和那個人搞好關係的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因為妳想忘記關於爸爸的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,步 請妳懂事點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我就是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙和前輩也在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有不去派對的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,明明派對那麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,偶爾也讓自己休息一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax Relax
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你最想見的人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 其實是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,吵架可不好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我能好好和她說就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,筋疲力盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,讓自己稍微放鬆一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要是不撐著我就要崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡就是這樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.15,0:16:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,現在也正處於這種時期
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你的家鄉是南斯拉夫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我的國家和家庭都已經消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我還有這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你們也還在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,託妳的福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是我錄的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 好好看好好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我是DJ KITE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,別擅自用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的唱片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,讓作者來刷碟更好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不能播放的唱片就只是個圓盤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,DJ春生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,春生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,已經沒有退路了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,再不開始觀眾就要生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,解放自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,日本最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,靜候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,去那邊聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,已經接受母親的儀式了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我這裡有個可以插隊的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,和我親熱起來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我這裡有後門可以讓妳走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這種就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不會弄疼妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.17,0:19:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,保證讓妳舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,神力女超人一擊就打倒了攻擊地球的異形
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到你吸了大麻會變成那種小屁孩性格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,異形是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不立刻離開日本呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那些有錢人好像都想逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,因為很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,即使失去了重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒有時間傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這太殘酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,悲傷也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣爸爸會生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.27,0:21:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,擦乾眼淚前進
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸經常說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,正因為有連自己的國家和家庭都回不去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才得忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我以後再也不會哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.87,0:22:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要動 舉起手來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,看樣子不是為了通知面會的時間而來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,果然在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.51,0:22:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,爺爺來接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.75,0:23:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,藥 藥
